			"widgets_values":[
				"A hand-drawn illustration-style fashion concept breakdown sheet in portrait orientation. The background features a soft beige parchment paper texture with subtle paper fiber details, evoking the quality of a high-end design sketchbook. The overall lighting is clean with soft shadows, and the image presents a high-quality 2D fashion magazine illustration aesthetic, perfectly balancing sophistication with a subtly sensual atmosphere.\n\nAt the center of the composition is a full-body illustration of a fashionable female character. Her pose is natural yet dynamic, with her weight on her right leg, left hand casually tucked into a trouser pocket, and right hand slightly raised to brush aside the wavy long hair near her ear, exuding confident charm. She wears a sharply tailored khaki mid-length belted trench coat over a black semi-sheer botanical floral lace fitted base layer that subtly reveals skin texture beneath; on the lower half, high-waisted slim-fit matte leather pants that outline smooth leg contours, and black pointed-toe stiletto ankle boots.\n\nSurrounding the central figure are structured breakdown panels and handwritten annotations distributed around the periphery, with all annotation text connected to corresponding areas by thin lines, rendered in dark gray handwritten font, bilingual in Chinese and English.\n\nThe upper left corner features an expression board area containing four side-by-side head close-ups:\nThe first expression is calm and confident with slightly upturned corners of the mouth, annotated: 'Neutral / 中性.'\nThe second expression shows slightly flushed cheeks with a slightly downcast gaze, annotated: 'Shy / 害羞.'\nThe third expression has widened eyes and slightly parted lips, annotated: 'Surprised / 惊讶.'\nThe fourth expression features a sharp gaze with slightly furrowed brows, annotated: 'Focused / 专注.'\n\nThe left side and lower left corner display layered clothing and fabric close-ups:\nA circular magnified view shows the trench coat cuff's buckle strap and stitching, annotated: 'Gabardine fabric / 华达呢面料.'\nA micro-magnification circle shows the delicate lace mesh and floral pattern of the inner base layer, annotated: 'Soft lace with floral pattern / 柔软植物纹蕾丝.'\nA rectangular frame shows the subtle sheen and surface undulation of the leather pants, annotated: 'Matte leather / 哑光皮革.'\nA hand close-up displays slender fingers wearing silver knuckle rings, annotated: 'Silver ring details / 银质戒指细节.'\n\nThe upper right side features a skin texture close-up:\nDisplaying the smooth skin shadows of the shoulder, neck, and collarbone area, annotated: 'Sk"
